---------------------------------------------------------------------------
                           Menüpunkt: Save World
---------------------------------------------------------------------------

If you want to save a world file to disk again, you can do this  with  this
option.  It  saves  the  current  world  under  it's  old name. You cannot,
however, overwrite the original levels.  Use  the  @{" Save World as... " link m00041f} menu
item, to save a world under a different name.

If this Menüpunkt is disabled, you either have selected the original  world
or  created  a new world and haven't given it a name using Save World as...
before.
