---------------------------------------------------------------------------
                            Menüpunkt: Iconify
---------------------------------------------------------------------------

Closes all windows and screens and creates a small application icon on  the
workbench  screen. Also flushes the filecache and the undo/redo buffer when
the @{" Flush Cache Iconified " link m03061f} Menüpunkt had been checkmarked.

